cs.LG, cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the sub-category of cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it deals with explaining neural network behavior. Additionally, the paper applies the proposed method on neural networks trained on language data, biological data, astronomy data, and medical data, which suggests that it may also belong to the sub-categories of cs.CL (Computation and Language), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
